{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_os3sW61Pkn7YsaeYinC6vSqr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"tool_EkXO8SVVEnKyCVtVN2wxMhSx","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Review implementation plan","prompt":"You are a plan-reviewer subagent. Review the implementation plan and PRD for ticket TST-001.\n\nCONTEXT:\n- Ticket: TST-001\n- Slug: fs-rbac-03-live-enforcement\n- PRD Path: aidd/docs/prd/TST-001.prd.md\n- Research Path: aidd/docs/research/TST-001.md\n\nTASK:\n1. Read the PRD file at aidd/docs/prd/TST-001.prd.md\n2. Read the research file at aidd/docs/research/TST-001.md (if exists)\n3. Review the implementation plan sections (milestones, phases, automation/checks)\n4. Identify any executable risks or blockers in the plan\n\nFOCUS AREAS:\n- Are the milestones realistic and well-defined?\n- Is there a clear dependency chain between phases?\n- Are there missing integration points?\n- Are the testing/validation strategies adequate?\n- Do the phases align with the PRD requirements?\n\nOUTPUT:\nProvide a structured review report with:\n- Overall verdict (PASS / WARN / BLOCK)\n- Key findings with severity\n- Specific recommendations for plan improvements","subagent_type":"feature-dev-aidd:plan-reviewer"}}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":26235,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":26235,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c9d8f772-fac0-4aa0-ba05-6715d2bcaffd","uuid":"c5478f28-26e4-4139-ae35-89b382f2cc35"}
