{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You are a prd-reviewer subagent. Review the PRD for ticket TST-001 for completeness and readiness.\n\nCONTEXT:\n- Ticket: TST-001\n- Slug: fs-rbac-03-live-enforcement\n- PRD Path: aidd/docs/prd/TST-001.prd.md\n\nTASK:\n1. Read the PRD file at aidd/docs/prd/TST-001.prd.md\n2. Review all PRD sections for completeness:\n   - AIDD:ANSWERS (should have Q1-Q5 answered)\n   - AIDD:DECISIONS (should reference Q1-Q5)\n   - AIDD:GOALS (should be specific and measurable)\n   - AIDD:ACCEPTANCE (should have clear AC-1, AC-2, AC-3)\n   - AIDD:METRICS (should be quantifiable)\n   - User scenarios (should cover main use cases)\n   - Functional requirements (checklist items)\n   - Non-functional requirements (performance, security)\n\nFOCUS AREAS:\n- Are all placeholder sections filled?\n- Are acceptance criteria testable?\n- Are metrics measurable?\n- Are user scenarios complete?\n- Is the PRD Review section at the bottom properly filled?\n\nOUTPUT:\nProvide a structured review report with:\n- Overall readiness verdict (ready / not_ready)\n- List of specific issues found\n- Recommendations to reach READY status"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"tool_FOjIvCGFFEWnRI2bMtf99ZbW","session_id":"c9d8f772-fac0-4aa0-ba05-6715d2bcaffd","uuid":"9453c305-c6df-4631-8652-2bf0ed53be05"}
